  "img": "icons/dice/d10black.svg",
  "description": "<p>When you taste new food, you may roll +heart or roll +iron to see if you can handle the spice level in this community. On a strong hit, it’s perfectly seasoned and others notice your good taste. On a weak hit, you must add some kind of seasoning or need the dish to be remade, which causes a few raised eyebrows, teasing, or minor social discomfort. On a miss, you can’t handle the flavors and embarrass yourself; lose 1 momentum or 1 spirit.</p><p>Alternatively, you may roll to determine the standard spice level for this community.</p>",
